{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the fascists-- there was a-- a-- a coup-- there was a coup by Count [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stahemberg ?] I think was his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember, when I was about 10 years old, and the socialists had built one of the-- the largest housing complexes in-- in Europe.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the first public housing complex, and it was a beautiful housing complex for that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was about oh, 15 minutes by train, by subway, from where I lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I could hear the machine guns they attacked-- when the fascists were attacking that housing pro-- project and during that coup.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I could hear, you know-- I could-- we could hear the machine guns going for a few days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we-- I remember not being on the street, not being allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, I don't think he himself ran the government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But then Dollfuss came in, and he was, I think, also part of the Catholic party.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he was murdered a few years afterwards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was murdered and shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so there was one upheaval after the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was never-- af-- after that first coup in 1932, maybe, there was never a period of-- of peace or-- or quiet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So you-- you never-- you never felt relaxed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You never felt that this was a good place to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there-- there weren't that many-- it all happened so quickly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it-- they were legalized very, very soon before-- just a few months before Hitler actually marched in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I might not have my dates very exact, but it might have been the end of '37 and Hitler marched in in March '38.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
